description:
The one thing that separates Jesus from any other god or claim to divinity is the fact that the tomb is empty and there is no body in any grave anywhere. Jesus rose from the dead in a miraculous act - death could not hold him and the stone was rolled back. Today it is remarkable to visit the tomb where he lay temporarily and cast our minds back to this event that brought such confusion to others in the moment. We can now look back on with such joy, hope and encouragement.
